sentences: Franck Rivoire (born March 21, 1984), better known by his stage name Danger,  is a French electronic musician.

In 2007, he signed to the label Ekler'o'shock because he enjoyed the music of its other artists such as DatA. There have since been four Danger EP's released on Ekler'o'shock as well as a number of remixes released both officially and otherwise.
